§7§oSearch "mythic processor" in JEI to find the list of machines!

§fThe easiest advantage to mythic machinery is very effective manufacturing! Right when I started thinking I'd have to upgrade my processing rates, how fortuitous!
This type of technology does open up a few more implications about what may be possible with more powerful magical abilities, and higher control over Recursion. 
If my theories on Dimensional Shards are correct, processing the amounts required to harness their power would indeed require incredibly efficient production lines, likely involving this type of machinery. The Arbiter, after all, was a powerful Recursive being, they had access to advanced technology, they were directly associated with Terra and the Testificates, and they were the main 'defender' of Dimensional Shards.
It is interesting how I am tracing back the steps of this figure so important to Terra's history, and I am fighting the same enemies...and the interest of the Meatball Man in me...
